item.title: Wenbin Tian
item.description:
• Position: Visting Student
  • Contact: N2409544F@e.ntu.edu.sg
  • Bio: Wenbin Tian is currently a Ph.D. student at the college of control science and engineering, Zhejiang University. She completed the bachelor’s degree in 2019 and subsequently earned the master’s degree in 2022, both from Chongqing University. Now she is a visiting student at NTU under Prof, Tan Rui, and research interest lies in time-sensitive networking.
